<div class="container">
    <h1 style="color: var(--text-color);">Daily Plan: Friday, January 16, 2026 (Week Wrap-Up)</h1>
    
    <div class="last-updated" style="color: var(--text-muted-color); font-size: var(--font-size-small);">
        <strong>Context:</strong> Week 3 Day 5 (Friday) | 
        <strong>Focus:</strong> Complete Features, Code Review, Prepare for Weekend | 
        <strong>Last Updated:</strong> 2026-01-16
    </div>

    <h2>Friday Goals: Finish Week Strong, Prepare for Next</h2>
    
    <div style="background: #e3f2fd; border-left: 4px solid #2196f3; padding: 15px; border-radius: 4px; margin: 20px 0;">
        <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">End-of-Week Checklist</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Finish Week's Work:</strong> Complete any ongoing Master Plan items</li>
            <li><strong>Code Review:</strong> Review all commits from Mon-Fri for quality</li>
            <li><strong>Test Suite:</strong> Run full test suite - verify nothing broken</li>
            <li><strong>Documentation:</strong> Update MASTER_PLAN_COORDINATION.tt with completion status</li>
            <li><strong>Next Week Plan:</strong> Identify which Master Plan items are next</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <h3>Week Summary Items:</h3>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Mon-Fri Work:</strong> What was completed? What was blocked?</li>
        <li><strong>Quality Metrics:</strong> Test pass rate, code coverage, performance</li>
        <li><strong>Git Log:</strong> Review all commits - ensure messages are clear</li>
        <li><strong>Blockers:</strong> Document any issues for Monday resolution</li>
    </ul>

    <div style="background: #d4edda; border-left: 4px solid #28a745; padding: 15px; border-radius: 4px; margin: 20px 0;">
        <h4 style="margin-top: 0;">Friday Wrap-Up Actions</h4>
        <ol>
            <li>Commit any outstanding changes</li>
            <li>Run test suite and verify passing</li>
            <li>Create Week 3 summary in session_history</li>
            <li>Update current_session.md with week completion</li>
            <li>Prepare handoff notes for Monday if needed</li>
        </ol>
    </div>

